This repo contains Python scripts to help automate the process of localizing content on a Zendesk Web portal.

The following article on the Zendesk website explains how to use the scripts in the "wp_initial_handoff" folder:

- Automating your first localization handoff (Web portal) - https://support.zendesk.com/entries/51237108

The scripts are based on custom automation scripts the docs team at Zendesk uses to localize the Zendesk documentation. The scripts are provided as a contribution to the community. They aren't part of the Zendesk product and aren't supported.